# Input

```scss
@#{$rule-name}   #{$value};

@unknown   #{meta.inspect($value)}{color:red}

@unknown fn({ width: 300px })   #{$query}{color:red}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@#{$rule-name} #{$value};

@unknown #{meta.inspect($value)} {
	color: red;
}

@unknown fn({ width: 300px })   #{$query} {
	color: red;
}

```
